<!--
    Brand mark used EVERYWHERE the product needs to identify itself:
      - adaptive-icon foreground (launcher)
      - system splash animated icon (Android 12+)
      - home-screen widget icon slot
      - any in-app "app logo" slot

    Geometry is perfectly symmetric along the vertical axis, so every launcher
    mask (circle, squircle, rounded-square, teardrop) gets the same optical
    balance — no "clipped on one side" feeling.

    Path is authored on a 108×108 viewport with the full mark inside the safe
    zone (24..84 in both axes per adaptive-icon spec).
-->
